<title>WHEN THE ROLL IS CALLED UP YONDER</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pathien pengkun ahunggita, phat tawpna ahungtun tieng,
 Kum khawtuong, vak leh hawih, zingkhuo avak tieng;
 Gal leh lama leia hukdamte a kikhawp tieng uleh,
 Chung lama min kilam tieng ziechun um ka.

[V2]
 Chunglama min kilam tieng leh (3)
 Chunglama min kilam tieng, zie chun um ka.

[V3]
 2. Zie zing khawvak hawih leh thieng a Isu a thite thawh tieng;
 A thawhkit lopina a chan tieng uleh;
 A mi telte van khela Ina a kikhawp tieng uleh,
 Chunglama min kilam tieng ziechun um ka.

[V4]
 3. Khawvak apat nitum chanin Lalpa di'n na sem ingka,
 A hehpih mak leh venna thu gen ingka;
 Chun, hinna a hung beih a, leia ka nasep ka zawh tieng,
 Chunglam a min kilam tieng ziechun um ka.</lyrics>
</song>